SIMPLE: unget
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unget
<hw>Un*get"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>get</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cause to be unbegotten
or unborn, or as if unbegotten or unborn.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I 'll disown you, I 'll disinherit you, I 'll <qex>unget</qex>
you.</q> <rj><qau>Sheridan.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ungifted</ent>⟦br⟧
